{"tid":819303,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"吳雨霏啲歌明明好好聽 但就唔紅","createTime":"2018-09-14T16:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T14:17:29.000Z","uid":182662,"like":90,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"90cc8750edbc89148808f16f914c33693db61b3f","tid":819303,"uid":182662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T16:29:53.000Z","msg":"首首歌既旋律都有唔同風格<br />\n就算係分手 失戀 單戀 背叛 被背叛 既sad歌都好<br />\n都係唔同既旋律風格<br />\n好多冷門歌 好好聽 但唔多人知<br />\n<br />\n蘇眉<br />\n一千個假想結局<br />\n水點<br />\n告白<br />\n生命樹<br />\n最幸福眼淚<br />\n最後一秒鐘<br />\n歸宿<br />\n流螢<br />\n<br />\n以上我覺得好好聽 而又唔相似既歌<br />\n次次唱k點歌都有人話未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢啲歌唔似而家啲歌手咁<br />\n例如 胡紅軍 許停亨 啲歌咁<br />\n雖然係好聽 但覺得首首都差不多 分唔出佢地邊首打邊首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a70f7c57d3d92832fb8f3a0a493abf3eb1173f","tid":819303,"uid":208726,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0e31593acb9f3bbca480d384edd1f4c2cd7f947","tid":819303,"uid":1562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T16:32:52.000Z","msg":"State of Mind 隻碟嗰8首歌<br />\n都值得推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9be081e21d6aad112313ebd94882f8f894d9efc","tid":819303,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T16:34:32.000Z","msg":"有冇咩單戀歌聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c1febb721e08519ef4fca478565376ed293db9","tid":819303,"uid":64438,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T16:35:42.000Z","msg":"很冷靜 知道我愛的 定把我當佈景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b10ae74c15e288c8fded354048b891792bc66c8","tid":819303,"uid":201018,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T16:35:57.000Z","msg":"我本人由出聽到宜家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid